           self-supporting metal foil about 1 mg/cm2 thick.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical error from the graphic bars
            For 2(1)+ states statistical accuracy was
            5% or better for angles below 40 grad.,
            3% or better for angles up to 110 grad and
            7% or better at larger angles.
            For 3-states statistical accuracy was
            15% or better for angle below 45 grad.,
            6% or better for angles up to 120 grad.
            and not worse than 25% at larger angles.
           For 2(2)+ states statistical accuracy ranges between 5%
           and 35%.
           For 4(1)+ state statistical accuracy was 6% or better.
           For 4(2)+, 6(1)+ and 6(2)+ statistical accuracy
           ranges between 8% and 40%.
STATUS     (CURVE,,F.Ballester+,J,NP/A,501,301,1989) Fig. 2
HISTORY    (20251214U) SD: BIB updated.
